  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The installation of 6 antennae would add further clutter to the roof top of Leroy House and consequently detract from the appearance of the host building. Furthermore, the proposed antennae would be visible in long views from St Paul's Road and Essex Road and would be detrimental to the character and appearance of the adjoining Canonbury Conservation Area. This would be contrary to Policies ENV1, C17, D1 and D4 of Islington's Unitary Development Plan 2002, Urban Design Guide 2006 and Conservation Area Design Guide 2002."
